.page-title
  %h2
    DJ Mon

  %p
    DJ Mon is a Rails engine based frontend for Delayed Job. It supports the #{link_to("ActiveRecord", "https://github.com/collectiveidea/delayed_job_active_record")} and #{link_to("Mongoid", "https://github.com/collectiveidea/delayed_job_mongoid")} Delayed Job backends.
    It also has an iPhone client.
  %p
    Installation and usage instructions are on the #{link_to "Github wiki", "https://github.com/akshayrawat/dj_mon"}. Feel free to #{link_to("report bugs", "https://github.com/akshayrawat/dj_mon/issues?state=open")} or #{link_to("send pull requests", "https://github.com/akshayrawat/dj_mon")}.

